00:23:00,465 --> 00:23:01,925
And the main purpose is to create

402
00:23:01,985 --> 00:23:03,546
some degree of variety in the player

403
00:23:03,586 --> 00:23:06,728
so that you give them some emotional journey that keeps

404
00:23:06,768 --> 00:23:07,889
players engaged in the game.

